entries.femaleVariant: And who do you think you'll be when you grow up?
I wanna be a combat medic! Like on TV!
That's lovely, sweetie! It's wonderful to save lives.
Uh-huh! And I'm gonna shoot all the cyberpsychos! That what's they do too! I saw it on dad's favorite show!
But I won't give them medicine. It's stupid to shoot someone first then save them!
Well, you are gonna have to work really hard to get onto the Trauma Team. They only take the best of the best, you know.
